bubblechart
title Risk Assessment Matrix with Criticality Colors
x-axis "Impact" 0 --> 10
y-axis "Likelihood" 0 --> 10
size-label "Exposure ($M)"
color-label "Criticality"
quadrants "Monitor,Review,Urgent,Critical"
quadrant-xmid 5
quadrant-ymid 5

colors
Critical : red
High : orange
Medium : yellow
Low : green
Informational : blue

data
System Outage    : 9.2, 9.2,  50, Critical
Data Breach      : 9.0, 7.5,  80, Critical
Vendor Failure   : 7.2, 7.8,  30, High
Regulatory Change: 6.5, 5.5,  25, High
Staff Turnover   : 5.8, 6.5,  15, Medium
Budget Variance  : 4.2, 4.8,  10, Medium
Minor Delay      : 3.5, 3.2,   5, Low
Documentation    : 2.1, 2.5,   2, Informational